Flaked is an American comedy web television series that stars Will Arnett , who developed it alongside the creator/executive producer of Arrested Development , Mitch Hurwitz .
The first season consisted of eight episodes , which were released simultaneously worldwide on March 11 , 2016 .
In July 2016 , the series was renewed for a six-episode second season , which is scheduled to premiere on June 2 , 2017 .
Columnist Cindy Elavsky describes the show as being about `` a self-help guru named Chip who 's struggling to stay a step ahead of his own lies . ''